{"type":"question","id":23272,"title":"如何看待日本乡民利用“习近平”三个字的谐音，提醒大家做好防护措施？","uid":29415,"topics":[32,6042,5262,136,266,120],"contents":"最近日本网上一直流行着的“三密”防护措施、被别出心裁的日本网友修改后，成了”集近闭”。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/f6gu4SG_d.webp?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/f6gu4SG_d.webp?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/f6gu4SG_d.webp?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n而日语中“集近闭”与“习近平”三个字读音相同，都是shuu kinn pei，可谓跟之前菲律宾的wuhan标语有异曲同工之妙，表现出了日本网友不但希望病毒退散也希望包子滚粗的心情，堪称乳包乳华的最好题材。","date":"2020-04-12","agreeCount":27,"discussionCount":8}